Inspired by @KevinColePFF's article on Aaron Rodgers, I used #nflverse win probability and examined how often QBs win when they have different win probabilities.

- Peyton/Brady a cut above the rest
- Rivers/Stafford underperform when favored
- Ben/Russ similar
